  "description": "A close-up macro shot focusing on the head of a dark-colored butterfly. The butterfly's compound eye is prominently displayed, appearing as a large, dark sphere with subtle reflections within. Fine, white, hair-like scales cover the butterfly's head and parts of its body. The butterfly's antennae are visible, sleek and black, extending upwards. The background is blurred and a warm, muted brown. The image highlights intricate details of the insect's anatomy.",
